{"tid":1156151,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"去完working holiday既你而家做緊咩","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T16:25:07.000Z","uid":196144,"like":61,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"871d87ef4c66e7fcd4b0b879b301a3bb65aa9ad9","tid":1156151,"uid":196144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"話哂人生得意須盡歡，出咗黎做野一段時間，<br />\n都唔知自己做緊咩，過得一日得一日咁，<br />\n愈黎愈覺得及時行樂既重要，<br />\n有啲想試下去working holiday，<br />\n想趁有時間，又無咩負擔既時候去下其他國家，<br />\n順便賺下錢，又可以更認識自己同其他人，<br />\n唯一卻步既係擔心返到黎又要重新面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下去過WH既你地返到黎既發展係點？<br />\n同埋覺得自己有咩改變？<br />\n如果唔識揸車，有無邊個地方唔好去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人一世點都要去一次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去黎都無咩改變 唔洗去"},{"pid":"3a6e1e940302b5f9efcd646f8162738f1faf4fc8","tid":1156151,"uid":213877,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"老豆係上市公司主席，去完WH返黎入左去幫手"},{"pid":"a33d2572eb43246bb3cd62e9f107d5312ec5a337","tid":1156151,"uid":196144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a6e1e940302b5f9efcd646f8162738f1faf4fc8","tid":1156151,"uid":213877,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"老豆係上市公司主席，去完WH返黎入左去幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"有父幹邊同啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4afe00595f16deae2172942a4ee06906c60b8bd","tid":1156151,"uid":154533,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"你本身有料既去無問題 番黎一樣有野做<br />\n你本身hea hea下既番黎一樣 唔敢講全部<br />\n但去都係識埋d on9台仔 洗下碗 做下農場 你想有咩大轉變<br />\n如果你想賺錢有working就唔會holiday"},{"pid":"77c9beed78d9806a32e5dca0443afe0ae05c81f5","tid":1156151,"uid":196144,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f4afe00595f16deae2172942a4ee06906c60b8bd","tid":1156151,"uid":154533,"like":40,"